pojo/Emp.java

    @Column(name = "gender", nullable = false, columnDefinition = "tinyint unsigned")
    @Comment("性别, 说明: 1 男, 2 女")
    private Short gender; //性别 , 1 男, 2 女

causes error:
...
Caused by: org.postgresql.util.PSQLException: ERROR: syntax error at or near "unsigned"


analysis:

PostgreSQL does not support the `unsigned` keyword in its column definitions

solution:
//  @Column(name = "gender", nullable = false, columnDefinition = "tinyint unsigned")
   @Column(name = "gender", nullable = false)


